Package org.knime.base.node.mine.pca

This package contains all classes for the PCA (principal component analysis) Node.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DialogComponentChoiceConfig
    Implementation of a dialog component for dimension selection in PCA configuration, used for SettingsModelPCADimensions.
    EigenValue

Package org.knime.base.node.mine.pca Description

This package contains all classes for the PCA (principal component analysis) Node. The node outputs the projection of the input columns to their principal components.
